Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.56,0:00:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这些到底是什么鬼东西\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What the shell are those things?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.23,0:00:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,不管它们是什么\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Whatever they were--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,现在都成废铜烂铁了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}they're junk now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.56,0:00:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大伙儿\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Guys,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,斯普林特\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Splinter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.13,0:00:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须找到斯普林特\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We've got to find Splinter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.71,0:00:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,斯普林特老师\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Master Splinter,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你能听见吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.97,0:00:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,多纳泰罗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Donatello,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你有没有办法...\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Donatello, any way to--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.26,0:00:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,龟壳电话\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Shell cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我在呼叫斯普林特老师\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'm calling Master Splinter
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,希望能行\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哪个键是接听键?\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}which button do you press to answer this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喂?\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,斯普林特老师 你还好吗?\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Master Splinter, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.37,0:00:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗?\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:00:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,斯普林特老师...\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Master Splinter...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的设备\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Stupid device.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:00:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你不用按任何按钮\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}you don't have to press any buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,已经接通了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You already answered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 李奥纳多\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Ah. Leonardo,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不管那些机器是什么\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}whatever those mechanical menaces are,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.69,0:01:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,它们已经啃穿了我们房子的支柱\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}they have managed to eat through the support structure of our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须马上离开\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We must leave right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,在南端的老下水道枢纽处汇合\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Meet me at the old drainage junction near South Point.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.94,0:01:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们走南边的管道\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}If we take the south conduit,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.28,0:01:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,它与旧的下水道有个交点\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}it'll intersect with the old drainage tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在那里与你会合 老师\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We'll meet you there, Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.51,0:01:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,他说什么? 他说什么了?\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}What'd he say? What'd he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,提到我了吗?\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Did he mention me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.79,0:01:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 开裂的水管\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Good-bye, broken pipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.61,0:01:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 脏兮兮的付费电话\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Good-bye, grungy pay phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 凹陷的井盖\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Good-bye, dented manhole cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.83,0:01:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,再见了 我甜蜜的家\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Good-bye, home, sweet home.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了 残酷的世界\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hello, cruel world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.06,0:01:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,看来那些东西来过这儿了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Looks like those things have been through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这些墙已经严重受损\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}These walls are seriously compromised.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.66,0:01:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,幸好屋顶还没塌下来\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It's lucky this roof hasn't caved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.87,0:01:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚说什么?\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You were saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没法前进 也没法后退\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Can't go forward. Can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,看来只能往上走了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Looks like we go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,去地面可不是好主意\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hitting the surface is a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.82,0:02:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有选择了 李奥\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We've got no other way to go, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.78,0:02:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我们只到下一个井盖就下去\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}but we're only going up to go down the next manhole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,明白吗? 不准乱逛\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Got it? No fooling around.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.29,0:02:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,记住老师说的话\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Remember what Sensei said.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.97,0:02:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,被人看到会很危险\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}It's dangerous for us to be seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,更别说被抓住了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}let alone captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要保持隐蔽\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We need to stay out of sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这话我们听了一千遍了 李奥\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We got it the first thousand times, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,跟着我走就是了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Just follow my lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.46,0:02:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,李奥 快上去\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Come on, Leo. Move it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想一直盯着你的屁股看\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I don't want to be staring at your butt any longer than I have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嘘 各位\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Shh. Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 发现井盖\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Ah, manhole cover,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.22,0:03:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,十二点钟方向\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}12 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,又怎么了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.34,0:03:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好极了 真是好极了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Great. Just great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,乌龟运气从不让人失望\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}The old turtle luck working true to form.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,隐蔽得真好 拉夫\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Way to be stealthy, Raph.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.68,0:03:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 新泽西都能听见你的动静了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Yeah. I don't think they heard you over in "Joisey."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.65,0:03:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,搭把手\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.84,0:03:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,想都别想 米奇\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Don't even think about it, Mikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.49,0:03:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,哎 懒得理你们\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Ah, forget you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己推\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}I'll push it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.66,0:03:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,老兄 真是大丰收\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Oh, man, what a score.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.00,0:03:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,快躲起来 拉夫\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hide, Raph.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 赶紧\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Come on. Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.74,0:03:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不好\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.95,0:04:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕的选择 拉斐尔\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Poor choice, Raphael.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看到那家伙的怂样了吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Did you see the way that guy squirmed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们抢他钱的时候\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}when we took his cash?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,像待宰的羔羊\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Sheep, man,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,被我们这群狼狠狠地宰\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}sheep to be fleeced by us wolves.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 天哪\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Oh, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,想象一下他们打开车门的时候会有多惊讶\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Imagine their surprise when they open the back of that truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,这正是斯普林特老师所说的情况\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}This is exactly what Master Splinter was talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.77,0:04:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须把他救出来\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We've got to get him out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.48,0:04:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一个到屋顶的是笨蛋\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Last one to the roof hatched from a rotten egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.78,0:04:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以在第三和第一大道截住他们\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}We can cut them off at Third and First.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们疯狂地跑的话\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}If we run like crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,难道有别的跑法吗\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Is there any other way to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 没错\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Ha ha! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.62,0:04:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你们太慢了\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}You guys are too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哦! 哦! 哦!\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Whoa! Whoa! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 春日般清新\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Mm, springtime fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.08,0:05:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,喔吼\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Whoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 老下水道枢纽\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Ah, the old drainage junction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.63,0:05:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我的孩子们在哪儿?\N{\fnArial\fs40\bord2}Now where are my sons?
